Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.82,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Awal dari segalanya dimulai
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.02,0:00:10.26,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,dengan kelahiran seorang bayi\Nyang bercahaya di Kota Qingqing, Tiongkok.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.24,0:00:13.44,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Dengan kelahiran bayi itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.00,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,mulai muncul kemampuan aneh\Nyang kemudian dikenal sebagai Quirk.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.88,0:00:20.86,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Jumlah orang yang lahir dengan kemampuan ini\Nterus meningkat setiap harinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.84,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Saat ini, sekitar 80 persen dari populasi dunia\Nmemiliki semacam Quirk,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.16,0:00:28.08,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,menjadikan dunia ini\Nsebagai masyarakat manusia super.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.32,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Di dunia yang kacau ini,\Nlahirlah sebuah profesi baru:
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.49,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Pahlawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.60,0:00:38.52,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Pahlawan adalah orang-orang terpilih
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.52,0:00:43.45,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,yang diakui oleh pemerintah dan menggunakan\NQuirk mereka untuk melayani masyarakat.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.42,0:00:47.16,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Akan tetapi, di zaman ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.16,0:00:49.38,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,ada juga pahlawan yang tidak seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.58,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Mereka yang tidak dipilih,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.58,0:00:55.22,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,tapi memilih bertindak sendiri,\NPahlawan Ilegal.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.10,0:00:58.26,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Apa sebenarnya keadilan bagi mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.82,0:01:01.86,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.22,0:01:05.19,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,apakah mereka pantas disebut pahlawan?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.10,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Ini adalah kisah
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.42,0:01:13.10,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,tentang seorang Vigilante\Nyang mengejar impian menjadi pahlawan sejati,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.52,0:01:18.24,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,sebelum Midoriya Izuku masuk ke SMA U.A.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.26,0:03:04.78,dialog,Villain,0,0,0,,Perutku... lapar!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.26,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Ada penjahat yang mengamuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.45,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Cepat lari!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.94,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Makan!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.00,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Gigi adalah segalanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.58,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.58,0:03:16.79,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Motorku!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.06,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Gawat...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.21,dialog,All Might,0,0,0,,Tenang saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.66,dialog,All Might,0,0,0,,Kenapa, kau tanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.26,dialog,All Might,0,0,0,,Karena aku sudah datang!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.78,dialog,All Might,0,0,0,,Rasakan ini, Penjahat!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.78,0:03:31.35,dialog,All Might,0,0,0,,Detroit Smash!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.22,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Wah, itu All Might!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.64,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Sekali pukul langsung beres!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.64,0:03:38.65,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Memang pantas jadi pahlawan nomor satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.84,0:03:44.74,dialog,All Might,0,0,0,,Semuanya, ada yang terluka?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.44,0:03:46.76,dialog,All Might,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak, syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.72,0:03:49.74,dialog,Villain,0,0,0,,Gigiku…
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.04,dialog,All Might,0,0,0,,Kau pengecualian!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.54,dialog,All Might,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.24,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,All Might...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.78,0:04:03.78,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kalau lihat langsung memang beda, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.62,0:04:06.62,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Aduh, gawat!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.90,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Aku akan telat ke universitas!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.72,0:04:16.92,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ma-Maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.66,0:04:18.78,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Dasar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.76,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Lihat apa yang telah kau lakukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.90,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Aku baru saja membeli ini.\NCepat minta maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.46,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Berlututlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.76,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,A-Aku benar-benar minta maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.62,dialog,Tokanatsu,0,0,0,,Bocah ini benar-benar berlutut.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.16,dialog,Tomonachi,0,0,0,,Apa dia tidak punya\Nharga diri sama sekali?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.76,0:04:37.80,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Dasar pecundang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.20,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Aduh!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.86,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Bocah sialan...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.68,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Jangan main-main denganku!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.94,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Berengsek!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.84,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Tunggu, dasar berengsek!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.34,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Haimawari Koichi,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.34,0:04:59.00,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,mahasiswa biasa\Nyang sibuk kerja paruh waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.36,dialog - atas,Narator,0,0,0,,Quirk-nya adalah "Meluncur".
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.16,dialog - atas,Narator,0,0,0,,Ia bisa bergerak seperti\Nmeluncur di permukaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.50,dialog - atas,Narator,0,0,0,,Syarat untuk mengaktifkannya:
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.20,dialog - atas,Narator,0,0,0,,Tubuhnya harus menyentuh permukaan\Ndengan tiga titik atau lebih.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.24,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Meski begitu, kecepatannya
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.98,0:05:12.90,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,cuma selevel sepeda biasa!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.76,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Oh, kayaknya Quirk tipe mobilitas, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.58,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Sepertinya lumayan praktis.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.38,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Tapi sepertinya tidak terlalu cepat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.24,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Agak menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.58,dialog,Narator,0,0,0,,Mirip kecoak.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.94,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Biarkan aku sendiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.56,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,♫Dengan hati yang POP♫
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.36,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,- ♫Dengan irama yang POP♫\N- POP Cantik!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.58,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,- ♫Akan kusampaikan perasaanku♫\N- POP Cantik!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.42,dialog - atas,Pop,0,0,0,,♫Kepadamu dengan POP dan HIP dan HOP♫
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.42,0:05:44.10,dialog - atas,Pop,0,0,0,,Semuanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.10,0:05:48.01,dialog - atas,Pop,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah datang lagi hari ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.62,0:05:53.28,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,♫Selamanya, sejak hari\Nyang penuh senyuman itu♫
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.28,0:05:59.65,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,♫Aku ingin bertemu denganmu,\NJadi aku terus menerus mencarimu♫
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.65,0:06:00.23,dialog,Fans,0,0,0,,Imut banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.23,0:06:06.24,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,♫Aku selalu memikirkanmu.\NJadikan suaraku ini sebagai pemandumu♫
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.24,0:06:12.53,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,♫Berharap kau akan menemukanku.\NDan memelukku erat♫
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.08,0:06:20.95,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,♫Bersinarlah terang! Berkilaulah!♫
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.96,0:06:26.15,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,♫P O P S T E P biarkan itu mencapaimu!♫
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.15,0:06:32.90,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,♫Bersinarlah terang! Berkilaulah!♫
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,- ♫Sekarang 1 2 3 dengan POP STEP Jump!♫\N- Pop☆Step gelar konser gerilya lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.10,0:06:39.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,- ♫Aku akan terbang ke arahmu♫\N- Semoga polisi tidak menangkapnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,- ♫Aku akan terbang ke arahmu♫\N- Lagunya biasa saja,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan makeup-nya mencolok,\Njadi mukanya tidak kelihatan jelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,- ♫Aku akan terbang♫\N- Tapi waktu itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,- ♫Aku akan terbang♫\N- dia terlihat sangat bersinar.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.58,0:06:49.14,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Itu karena dia terbang di udara.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.24,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Enak sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.48,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Quirk "Lompatan" itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.10,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Gawat, waktunya kerja paruh waktu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.80,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Manusia selalu mengagumi\Napa yang mereka lihat dari bawah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.74,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Sebaliknya, jika kau\Nmenundukkan pandanganmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.02,0:07:18.78,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,kau akan benar-benar dipandang rendah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.80,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hidup itu
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.40,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,memang tidak adil, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.78,0:07:34.44,dialog,Manajer,0,0,0,,Waktu keterlambatanmu,\Naku potong dari gajimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.63,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.72,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Akhirnya tetap telat juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.26,0:07:39.98,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Selamat datang...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.98,0:07:40.72,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Sial.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.72,0:07:42.29,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Lain kali kalau ketemu lagi...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.00,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Si kecoak.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.76,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Spike itu Quirk-ku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.38,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Kalau ditusuk sangat sakit, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.66,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Takut, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.66,0:07:57.70,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Rasakan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.20,0:08:02.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Rasakan ini.\N- Dasar pengecut!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.92,0:08:11.80,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Sial.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.50,0:08:13.92,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ada apa dengan orang-orang itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.87,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kenapa polisi tidak melakukan apa pun?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.88,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ini membuatku sangat kesal.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.09,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Aku sangat frustrasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.41,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Sudah kuputuskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.04,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Malam ini, aku akan melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.70,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mengenakan kostum spesialku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.42,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Aku akan menggunakan Quirk-ku sesuka hati,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.90,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,melampiaskan semua kekesalan di hatiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.76,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hukum tidak penting.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.92,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Aku akan lakukan apa saja sebisaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.52,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Oh, target sudah kelihatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.28,0:08:44.46,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kau menjatuhkan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.62,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Halte bus malam ada di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.24,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Masih 10 menit lagi\Nsebelum kereta terakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.46,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.87,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Dia lagi beraksi, nih, si Nice Guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.14,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Wah, baik banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.42,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Benar-benar baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.37,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Nice Guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.32,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus, Nice Guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.50,0:09:10.56,dialog,Warga,0,0,0,,Tolong buangkan sampah rumahku\Nsekalian pas pulang, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.82,0:09:15.82,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Rasanya puas sekali\Nsetelah berbuat baik sepuasnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.16,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Fiuh, aku kelelahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.68,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Tenggorokanku kering.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.44,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Ini, silakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.31,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.35,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Eh? Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.56,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,POP☆STEP?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.96,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.54,0:09:33.32,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kau orang yang sering membantu\Nmemungut sampah di jalan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.50,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak salah namamu...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.42,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Pria kecoak?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.42,0:09:37.74,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Namaku Nice Guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.18,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Jaket hoodie norak itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.16,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,kau cosplay All Might, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.14,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Betul.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.68,0:09:47.64,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Aku ingin menjadi seperti dia,\Nsebisa mungkin berkontribusi bagi dunia.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.62,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Selain itu, ini tidak norak.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.63,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ini sangat keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.16,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.16,0:09:53.40,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Sebisa mungkin, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.38,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Kau tahu batas kemampuanmu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.58,0:09:57.26,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ya, itu benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.60,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mengerti batas kemampuan itu penting.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.44,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Jadi, kau Limit Man, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.68,0:10:00.78,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Namaku Nice Guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.38,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kalau kau bermain pura-pura\Njadi idola terlalu jauh,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.74,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,polisi akan menangkapmu jadi hati-hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.25,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Oh, dan terima kasih untuk minumannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.64,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.68,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Ini bukan sekadar bermain!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.68,0:10:12.50,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Aku serius!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.30,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Aduh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.30,0:10:13.98,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.98,0:10:14.96,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.88,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan, gadis sialan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Jangan.\N- Ada apa dengan gadis ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.24,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Pakaiannya di balik mantelnya\Nterbuka sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.50,dialog,Tokanatsu,0,0,0,,Dia mesum!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.50,0:10:24.90,dialog,Toji,0,0,0,,Aku kenal dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.90,0:10:28.28,dialog,Toji,0,0,0,,Dia Siswi SMA Pamer Pantat yang terkenal\Ndi internet, wanita yang tidak senonoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.28,0:10:31.00,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Dengan cat tubuh itu...\Napakah dia mencoba menjadi pahlawan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.44,dialog,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Lebih mirip penjahat!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.90,0:10:33.88,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Aku tidak menunjukkan wajahku di depan umum!\N- Itu... itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.88,0:10:38.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, kita foto wajah aslimu\Ndan unggah ke internet saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.64,0:10:40.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau jahat sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.58,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hei! Berhentilah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.36,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kalian...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Kau ini kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan urusanmu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enyahlah, dasar hoodie kampungan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan... itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.16,0:10:52.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak kampungan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.60,0:10:57.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Me-Memang ini bukan urusanku...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.64,0:10:58.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku permisi dulu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.85,0:11:01.54,dialog,Pop,0,0,0,,Hentikan ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.84,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,A-Aku bukan hoodie kampungan,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.38,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,juga bukan Limit Man.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.94,0:11:11.20,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Aku pria yang tidak bisa berpaling\Nsaat melihat orang lain dalam kesulitan,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.68,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Nice Guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski aku tidak pandai berkelahi...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Apa yang kau bicarakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.72,0:11:18.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau serangan mendadak!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.18,0:11:20.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.92,0:11:30.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini? Kalau dilihat-lihat,\Nbukankah ini teman lama kita?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ngapain sok-sokan maju?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.60,0:11:35.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau cuma seekor kecoak.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih menganggap dirimu pahlawan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakit sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, sudah kuputuskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan menghajarmu begitu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menghancurkanmu dan toserba itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.32,0:11:47.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai berkeping-keping!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.17,0:11:53.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekalian menelanjangi wanita mesum ini\Ndan mengaraknya di jalanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.96,dialog,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ke-Kenapa sampai sejauh itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja karena kau\Nmembuatku sangat kesal!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan memanggil polisi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.14,0:12:09.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lupakan itu,\Nbukankah lebih baik memanggil pahlawan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Coba bilang, "Tolong aku, All Might!"
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, coba teriak!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.74,0:12:18.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,All Might tidak punya waktu\Nuntuk mengurusi ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo. Kenapa diam saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.36,0:12:28.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak peduli seberapa keras\Nkita berteriak minta tolong saat ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.22,0:12:32.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin dia akan terbang datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.26,0:12:37.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada orang jatuh dari langit?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi kalian membicarakan All Might, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak akan datang ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.42,0:12:52.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ada di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.69,0:12:55.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.95,0:12:59.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun pendaratannya agak jelek,\Ntapi tidak perlu khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam keadaan darurat,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,tempat sampah jadi bantalan yang lumayan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.07,0:13:06.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama lehermu sudah terlatih dengan baik,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.43,0:13:10.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,risiko cedera tulang belakang leher\Ndan gegar otak bisa dikurangi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.97,0:13:14.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Apa-apaan paman ini...?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan tiba-tiba?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertanya siapa aku\Ndan apa yang akan aku lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, akan kujawab dengan benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Knuckleduster.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.53,0:13:39.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pembersih yang ahli\Ndalam sampah sepertimu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman ini sudah gila, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.65,0:13:48.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak berubah warna.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan yang kucari, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang ini juga bukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.81,0:14:06.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Nak.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.35,0:14:10.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Aku tidak ada hubungannya\Ndengan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.63,0:14:12.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau punya potensi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku butuh bantuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bantu aku dengan pekerjaanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.97,0:14:19.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan membuatmu menjadi pahlawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.05,0:14:23.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudku, aku tidak tertarik\Ndengan hal semacam itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Aku permisi dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.25,0:14:27.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bohong.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.57,0:14:31.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menghormati All Might,\Ndan membantu orang adalah hobimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.97,0:14:35.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu kau bilang kau tidak tertarik\Ndengan pekerjaan pahlawan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.93,0:14:41.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan Quirk-ku yang payah, tidak mungkin\Naku bisa memenuhi lisensi sebagai pro.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa? Maksudku...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.75,0:14:49.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Quirk yang kuat dan lisensi profesional...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.52,0:14:53.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua itu sebenarnya tidak ada hubungannya\Ndengan keadilan sejati.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat dihadapkan pada sesuatu\Nyang harus dilakukan,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,apakah kita bisa bergerak atau tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persyaratan jiwa pahlawan
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,hanya satu hal saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kata lain,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman ini tidak punya lisensi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bercanda.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan sok bicara soal keadilan,\Ndasar tua bangka.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sarankan jangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.71,0:15:19.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinjuku tidak akan melemah\Nhanya karena ada sandera.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan sandera.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.33,0:15:24.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menggunakan Spike\Ndan tusuk wajah wanita ini sampai hancur.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.21,0:15:29.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Aku tidak puas kalau tidak melakukannya!\N- Jangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Lepaskan aku!\N- Saat dihadapkan
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,pada sesuatu yang harus dilakukan…
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah bisa bergerak atau tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.19,0:15:40.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang diuji oleh jiwa pahlawan adalah
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.97,0:15:43.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,hanya satu hal saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus, Nak.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.71,0:16:12.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata semuanya\Nmemang bukan target yang tepat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.73,0:16:15.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, demi berjaga-jaga,\Nidentitas mereka harus dipastikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.55,0:16:21.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nak,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.71,0:16:25.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan kujelaskan perlahan seperti apa\Nrasanya bekerja sebagai pahlawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.39,0:16:29.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memukul penjahat itu... sangat memuaskan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.77,0:16:34.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menolak tawaranmu\Ndengan sekuat tenaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat itu yang terlintas di kepalaku,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,bukan "terima kasih"\Natau "aku terselamatkan",
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.57,0:16:45.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,melainkan "muncul orang yang lebih berbahaya".
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, bicara soal orang berbahaya itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haimawari Koichi, 19 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mahasiswa tahun pertama\NUniversitas Hitonami.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Itu kan kartu mahasiswaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dompetku juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku panggil Koichi saja
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,atau panggil Nice Guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong jangan buka-buka tanpa izin!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Panggil aku "guru" saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang,\Naku tidak berniat jadi muridmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.47,0:17:12.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus, tolong keluar dari rumahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.45,0:17:16.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini?\NDi kulkas hanya ada teh barley?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, ada bir.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu untuk senior kampusku kalau datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak-anak muda tidak seharusnya minum.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.82,0:17:24.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Disita.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sama sekali\Ntidak mendengarkanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.85,0:17:33.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bercanda, Berengsek.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.07,0:17:37.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suatu hari nanti, aku pasti akan\Nmenghabisi kecoak dan tua bangka itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan, sebaiknya jangan cari gara-gara\Ndengan orang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian terluka parah, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.49,0:17:48.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.51,0:17:55.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku punya obat yang bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.07,0:18:00.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sedang memburu obat terlarang\Nyang beredar di kota ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu obat...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betul.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Obat berbahaya jenis baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nama obat itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.81,0:18:13.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Trigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Obat ini melemahkan kendali diri,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan meningkatkan kekuatan Quirk pengguna.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.09,0:18:23.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kata lain, itu obat yang bisa\Nmengubah orang biasa menjadi penjahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini sangat luar biasa!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dibiarkan,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.57,0:18:38.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,kota ini akan dipenuhi penjahat dadakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa didiamkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.31,0:18:44.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi bukankah sebaiknya hal seperti ini\Ndiserahkan ke polisi atau para pahlawan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tidak bisa mengandalkan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penjahat dadakan\Nyang disebabkan oleh Trigger
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.67,0:18:51.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,muncul begitu saja dari tengah keramaian.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.79,0:18:55.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Polisi atau pahlawan pro\Nhanya bisa setelah kejadian terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itulah kita\Nyang harus turun tangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Barusan kau bilang "kita"?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.39,0:19:02.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betul.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau dan aku akan menghentikan\Norang-orang mencurigakan
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan memeriksa lidah mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lidah?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.23,0:19:10.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengguna tetap Trigger mengalami efek samping\Nyang membuat lidah mereka berubah warna.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi kehitaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.33,0:19:17.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makanya waktu itu\Nkau melihat lidah mereka ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betul.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau lidahnya hitam, langsung hajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita paksa keluar informasi soal bandar,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu putus jalur distribusinya dari akar!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.79,0:19:26.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Langsung dihajar begitu aja?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serangan duluan lebih baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.45,0:19:33.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selesaikan sebelum para pecandu\Nsempat menyuntik Trigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masalahnya, kalau kita minta lihat lidah,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,kemungkinan besar bakal ditolak, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.95,0:19:39.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau sudah kelihatan mencurigakan\Ndan menolak, langsung hajar juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bercandaanmu tidak lucu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.81,0:19:45.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benar-benar mengira kau bercanda,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi ternyata bukan, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian sedang meributkan apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.59,0:19:52.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,POP☆STEP.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begini, sebenarnya sekarang...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi kalian sedang mencari pecandu\Ndan pengedar obat?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, terima kasih untuk yang kemarin,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.25,0:20:08.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku tidak akan lupa,\Npaman sempat mau tinggalkan aku begitu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terserah kau saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.01,0:20:13.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, Nice Guy...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.65,0:20:14.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Panggil aku Koichi saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, itu nama asli?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, Koichi,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.13,0:20:20.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,kenapa kau menemaninya\Nmelakukan hal seperti itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kok, kau diam saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.87,0:20:26.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.65,0:20:27.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.55,0:20:31.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya berpikir jika dibiarkan,\Ndia pasti akan menyerang orang di jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.85,0:20:34.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya memukul mereka\Nyang benar-benar mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti anak muda\Nyang bergaya nyentrik itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.71,0:20:37.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terasa sangat asal-asalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua, coba pakai otak sedikit?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penjahat yang muncul di jalan itu
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.83,0:20:47.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,pasti akan direkam oleh seseorang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinggal cari pakai kata kunci\Nkayak "penjahat baru"
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.59,0:20:53.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,atau "penjahat tiba-tiba" untuk mencari,\Nlalu tentukan lokasinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habis itu baru deh, diinterogasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, kau pintar sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.15,0:20:57.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.07,0:20:58.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Hah, lagi?!\N- Kau! Yang di situ!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.51,0:21:00.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunjukkan lidahmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.35,0:21:02.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tu-Tunggu sebentar!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.25,0:21:06.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dilihat bagaimanapun, bukankah orang ini\Nhanya pekerja kantoran biasa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunjukkan lidahmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.67,0:21:14.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah ini boneka mainan anak-anak?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang dewasa yang sudah tua\Nmasih membawa boneka di jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.33,0:21:23.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di internet banyak orang dewasa\Nyang koleksi begituan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.21,0:21:25.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ini sebenarnya sales mainan, jadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.73,0:21:30.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, dia orang biasa\Nyang bekerja dengan serius.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.59,0:21:32.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan segera tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama, buat dia tidak bisa melawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.89,0:21:40.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menggunakan kekerasan di depan umum...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.21,0:21:42.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengerikan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.25,0:21:46.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini "penjahat dadakan"\Nyang lagi sering muncul, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.97,0:21:49.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pahlawan Penghapus,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eraser Head, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.74,0:23:27.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo, semuanya, aku Haimawari Koichi.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.88,0:23:30.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun tidak memiliki lisensi,\Naku mulai melakukan kegiatan kepahlawanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.70,0:23:33.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nama pahlawanku adalah The Crawler.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.12,0:23:36.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang seperti ini\Nmalah terseret ke dalam kasus besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.32,0:23:38.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya, "Lepas Landas".
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.12,0:23:39.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ingin terbang!
